  "prompt": "How is work life balance in wipro consumer care and lighting?",
  "response": "Work-life balance at Wipro Consumer Care and Lighting can vary based on factors such as job role, department, and individual management styles. Generally, Wipro is known for promoting a healthy work-life balance and often implements policies that support flexible working arrangements, employee wellness programs, and various initiatives to improve the overall work environment.\n\nEmployees may experience different levels of work-life balance depending on specific project demands, deadlines, and team culture. Some employees might find a flexible work schedule beneficial, while others may face challenges related to workload or project timelines.\n\nFor the most accurate and detailed information, it might be helpful to look at employee reviews on platforms like Glassdoor or seek insights from current or former employees of Wipro Consumer Care and Lighting.",
